<#include "Base.ftl">

<#macro head>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@700&family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,700&display=swap"
          rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="templates/ftl/css/rescentre.css">
</#macro>

<#macro content>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="profile">

        <div class="box">
            <h3>What is this site?</h3>
            <div class="content">
                <p>We are Moneysave - a large project,
                    thanks to which you can
                    to distribute funds correctly.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h3>How can Moneysave help me?</h3>
            <div class="content">

                <p>On the site you can read
                    your income and expenses. This requires
                    just go to the special tab.
                    After that you will have access to a convenient diagram,
                    which shows your budget.</p>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h3>Why should I choose this particular site?</h3>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Moneysave is a very fast and user-friendly site. Eventually
                    in a couple of clicks you can create your own diagrams,
                    add new categories, chat with friends.</p>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h3>How can I create a chart to calculate my budget?</h3>
            <div class="content">
                <p>To do this, just click on the "Diagram" tab and you
                    will be immediately transferred to the page,
                    where you can easily create a chart with the categories you need.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h3>Can I create my own categories?</h3>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Of course, for this you need to go to the "Diagram" tab.
                    There you will be available window “Category name”,
                    in which you can write the name of the category.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h3>Can I chat with other users?</h3>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Yes, just go to your personal account.
                    There will be a button - "Chat".
                    Here you can discuss not only the past day, but also
                    your earnings per day or spending per month.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    </div>
</#macro>
